query: SELECT COUNT(*) AS CYCLEJ_I_TRANSACTIONS FROM PCJRDB01.TBL_JR_CJ_METRIC A INNER JOIN PCNFDB01.TBL_NF_CYCLEDATE B ON A.MTRC_CYCLE_DT = B.CYDT_CYCLE_DT AND A.MTRC_COMPANY_NO = B.CYDT_COMPANY_NO WHERE A.MTRC_BUS_INTENT_ID = 'BCC' AND A.MTRC_COMPANY_NO = '01' WITH UR
